<h1>Audit (A-05-12-00042)</h1>

<h2>02-08-2013<br />
Indiana Improperly Claimed Federal Reimbursement for All Reviewed Medicaid Inpatient Psychiatric Hospital Service Payments to Logansport State Hospital</h2>

<h2 class="line">Complete Report</h2>

